we've set, it's actually a very very simple
set up, all just around slightly

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:14.219
above mid way really. So bass, mid and treble,
just slightly above mid way. It's a really

00:01:14.219 --> 00:01:21.219
simple sound. Really just letting the sound
