Now you can adjust that to get a jazzier sound. So
all you'd need to do would be to adjust the

00:01:29.509 --> 00:01:35.640
treble control. Sort of down to a really really
low level will give you a warm sound.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:40.140
You may want to tweak the mid range a little if
