you may need to adjust this depending on how
your amp sounds. You may need to go a little

00:02:26.459 --> 00:02:30.680
higher or even a little lower. But the main
thing with this sound is that the gain is

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:37.370
actually surprisingly low. So err on the side
