00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:58.000
the middle position settings, so the bass
we've set right in the middle. You may find

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.870
if you haven't got quite such a big meaty
speaker cabinet as we're using, you might

00:03:01.870 --> 00:03:06.670
want to use a little bit more bass to get
a similar tone. And in terms of middle and

00:03:06.670 --> 00:03:11.959
treble we've just set those a little way past
the middle, a little bit of extra boost there

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:18.360
and that'll help you cut through and give
